Subject: Introduction to Machine Learning with Python

Subject: Philosophy in Anime
Description: Sword Art Online asks us 'Is the real world virtual?' Ghost in the Shell asks us 'Who has a soul, and what makes us human (or cyborg)?' Avatar asks us 'What is good?' while Psyco-Pass asks us 'When is society a trap?' Come explore these thought-provoking questions posed by Anime!  Speakers include:Cassy Sinke, Richard Herrell, BluRaven Houvener - Track: Anime  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
